#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you plan to practice your vocabulary regularly, you should make sure "
#| "that the <emphasis>Blocking</emphasis> feature is enabled. Go to the "
