#| "from the options shown. In the new field write <guilabel>Fruits</"
#| "guilabel> and hit the &Enter; key again."
msgid ""
"We now rename <guilabel>Lesson 1</guilabel> to <guilabel>Animals</guilabel> "
"and then we add a unit called <guilabel>Fruits</guilabel>. Click with the "
"&RMB; on the <guilabel>Lesson 1</guilabel> and choose <guimenuitem>Rename "
"Unit</guimenuitem> from the items shown. Now <guilabel>Lesson 1</guilabel> "
"is highlighted and you can simply overwrite it by typing in "
"<guilabel>Animals</guilabel>. When done, press the &Enter; key. Now click "
"with the &RMB; on the <guilabel>Collection: Vocabulary trainer E...</"
"guilabel>, which is the root of the unit tree and choose <guimenuitem>New "
"Unit</guimenuitem> from the items shown. In the new field write "
"<guilabel>Fruits</guilabel> and press the &Enter; key again."
msgstr ""
"Anname nüüd <guilabel>üksusele 1</guilabel> nimeks <guilabel>Animals</"
"guilabel> ning lisame seejärel üksuse nimega <guilabel>Fruits</guilabel>. "
"Tee paremklõps kirjel <guilabel>Üksus 1</guilabel> ja vali <guilabel>Muuda "
"üksuse nime</guilabel>. Kirje <guilabel>Üksus 1</guilabel> on nüüd esile "
"tõstetud ning sa võid selle lihtsalt üle kirjutada, sisestades "
"<guilabel>Animals</guilabel>. Kui oled valmis, vajuta klahvi &Enter;. Nüüd "
"tee paremklõps üksuste puu juurelemendil <guilabel>Kogu: Vocabulary trainer "
"E...</guilabel> ning vali <guilabel>Uus üksus</guilabel>. Kirjuta uuele "
"väljale <guilabel>Fruits</guilabel> ja vajuta taas klahvi &Enter;."

